### POST water a tree
# "timestamp":"{{$datetime "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss.ms"}}",
POST {{API_HOST}}/post
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "queryType":"water",
    "time":"2022-11-17T14:11:59.857Z",
    "timestamp":"2022-11-17T14:11:59.857Z",
    "tree_id":"{{TREE_ID}}",
    "uuid": "{{USER_ID}}",
    "username":"{{USER_NAME}}",
    "amount": 100
}

### Adopt a tree

POST {{API_HOST}}/post
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "queryType":"adopt",
    "tree_id":"{{TREE_ID}}",
    "uuid": "{{USER_ID}}"
}

